document.discussion_title: Clinton jumps ahead in polls in key states
document.topic_text: Home » News » Clinton jumps ahead in polls in key states Clinton jumps ahead in polls in key states Submitted: 08/22/2016 - 3:21am With less than three months until the general election, a new CBS News Battleground Tracker poll shows Hillary Clinton leading Donald Trump in key battleground states. CBS News Elections Director Anthony Salvanto joins CBS Weekend News to discuss what Clinton’s leads means for the presidential race as election day approaches. Share:
